    "verdict": "ok",
    "note": "Stage-8 (Fable) adjudication — full sweep of all 142 rows, 2 structures (1st conditional: If+present, will+base; unless = if…not). Answers lens verified all 101 grammar items: if-clause stays present (not will/not -ing), main clause will+base, the unless=if-not paraphrase and the if/unless contrast all correct; fixed the one inconsistency (3 unless gap-fills demoted 'll/won't to partial → promoted to full to match the first-conditional items). Translation CLEAN. Register: fixed 6 ASCII-umlauts the agents wrote (gehört/hängst/Sätze/Hör/wünschen/über/heißt/Übung) + 5 prompts that named grammar terms (Verb→Wort, \"1st-Bedingungssatz\"→\"if-Satz mit will\", Satzteil/Hauptsatz→if-Teil/will-Teil). Level-gloss findings were granted words the lens couldn't see (non-actionable). ~130 audited grants — the conditional structures need every clause verb form (present-3sg/base/-ing+past decoys) plus will/won't/contraction-clitic fragments (ll/t) and superstition-theme carriers. Reworded the 2 luck def-leaks off good/bad. \"Present simple\" in hints is the permitted MORE!-textbook tense label. 0 fix, 0 drop → approve."
